{"tid":2413924,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"當局收逾40份廣播處長職位申請　接見7人無一合適","createTime":"2021-02-19T05:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T05:11:04.000Z","uid":362414,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e3500758e1b6ed53734a0b826d1cc77d9718499","tid":2413924,"uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局常任秘書長梁卓文表示，政府與廣播處長梁家榮的合約於8月完結，雙方經討論後同意提前幾個月完結。他表示，薪金都是按合約條款安排，政府希望致力於港台內部培養接任人員及晉升，而內部無合適人選之下，當局就進行公開招聘，透過獵頭公司收到41份申請，甄選委員會見過7人，但並無合適人選。<br />\n<br />\n梁卓文表示，在考慮政府內部人選方面，新任處長李百全是資深政務官，行政經驗豐富，形容是合適人選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576393-20210219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576393-20210219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69M3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=dc4de5a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576393-20210219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=47a0dbf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576393-20210219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"18031c8a2ac33d93430af1a9e720418ae18b8e51","tid":2413924,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:08:44.000Z","msg":"港台要學哈利波特對付恩不里居教授咁對付呢條友"},{"pid":"955778684ec661bf20988e44856cbd8dc1af6227","tid":2413924,"uid":123848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"專程想請個廢物<br />\n真係好難選"},{"pid":"c5fccf8407ac7d8112910e22ab931145f456aab7","tid":2413924,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"in乜撚嘢呀<br />\n全世界都知係欽點"},{"pid":"8cfd8d7af6d4bb19a550958c245764eb8f609000","tid":2413924,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"港台內部點會冇人合適"}]}